    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238810/extras/21b5995f6b53fd8eb885f33f9f615c06.webp?t=1761936852\" width=620 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238810/extras/1367890b01be67c93087a093d820f652.poster.avif?t=1761936852\" width=534 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238810/extras/1367890b01be67c93087a093d820f652.webm?t=1761936852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238810/extras/1367890b01be67c93087a093d820f652.mp4?t=1761936852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;9 lives 9 Millimeters&quot; is a single or multi-player tower defense game where the player(s) mix and match weapons, appliances, food, and cat cards to serve customers and take out vermin. Players must defend their territory and their customers from bugs that evolve over time and keep the customers happy. More coffee! Players must rethink their strategy as the game progresses and upgrade their cats. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238810/extras/32343b45480bbff91e1141714b933d52.poster.avif?t=1761936852\" width=558 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238810/extras/32343b45480bbff91e1141714b933d52.webm?t=1761936852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238810/extras/32343b45480bbff91e1141714b933d52.mp4?t=1761936852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine cards to create new towers such as lions. Develop the cats to sniper kitties and other advanced weaponry to stop the brutal onslaught of these bugs from encroaching on the cafe and from stealing the customers, 9 in total.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238810/extras/54e7d3c7fcfa6fb3ad212337e7615815.poster.avif?t=1761936852\" width=558 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238810/extras/54e7d3c7fcfa6fb3ad212337e7615815.webm?t=1761936852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238810/extras/54e7d3c7fcfa6fb3ad212337e7615815.mp4?t=1761936852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > At the same time, don't let the customers go thirsty. Deliver coffee and make money. Satisfy customers and murder bugs to buy cards, build refrigerators, blow up stoves, and upgrade towers to crush this menace to society. How long can the player(s) keep the customers alive... and paying?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgradable units such as cats, refrigerators, and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable loadouts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy card packs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine cards for surprises</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wide variety of cats and weapons</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>It's cats vs. bugs and your nine lives are running out.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238810/extras/21b5995f6b53fd8eb885f33f9f615c06.webp?t=1761936852\" width=620 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p>",
